## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-102">XML 結構描述項目定義名為`xsi:choice`用來定義複雜的項目可以包含執行個體中的只有一個子系 (maxoccurs = 1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-102">The XML schema element definition named `xsi:choice` is used to define a complex element that can contain only one child in an instance (maxoccurs = 1).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-103">子系可以是數種類型，其中，它可以有數個名稱之一。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-103">That child can be one of several types, and it can have one of several names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-104">每個名稱會與特定的型別; 相關聯不過，多個名稱可以是相同的型別相關聯。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-104">Each name is associated with a specific type; however, several names can be associated with the same type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-105">因為這個緣故，這類項目的執行個體則是剪報等項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-105">Because of this, an instance of such an element is indistinct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-106">例如，請考慮下列會定義名為這類剪報等元素的結構描述片段`MyChoice`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-106">For example, consider the following schema fragment that defines such an indistinct element named `MyChoice`.</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceOne" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceTwo" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-107"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>可讓您將特殊的列舉值指派給成員的每個執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-107">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> allows you to assign a special enumeration value to each instance of the member.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-108">您必須是列舉型別自行建立，或可以藉由產生[XML 結構描述定義工具 (Xsd.exe)](~/docs/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-108">You must either create the enumeration yourself or it can be generated by the [XML Schema Definition Tool (Xsd.exe)](~/docs/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe.md).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-109">下列 C# 程式碼示範如何<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>套用至`Item`欄位;<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A>屬性會識別包含列舉型別可進一步用來偵測選擇的欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-109">The following C# code shows how the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to an `Item` field; the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property identifies the field that contains the enumeration that is further used to detect the choice.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class Choices{  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ItemType")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceOne")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceTwo")]  
 public string MyChoice;  
  
 // Do not serialize this next field:  
 [XmlIgnore]  
 public ItemChoiceType ItemType;  
}  
// Do not include this enumeration in the XML schema.  
[XmlType(IncludeInSchema = false)]  
public enum ItemChoiceType{  
 ChoiceOne,  
 ChoiceTwo,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-110">就地這段程式碼時，您可以序列化和還原序列化這個類別，藉由設定`ItemType`欄位設為適當的列舉型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-110">When this code is in place, you can serialize and deserialize this class by setting the `ItemType` field to an appropriate enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-111">例如，若要序列化`Choice`類別，C# 程式碼如下所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-111">For example, to serialize the `Choice` class, the C# code resembles the following.</span></span>  
  
```  
Choices mc = new Choices();  
mc.MyChoice = "Item Choice One";  
mc.ItemType = ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-112">還原序列化時，C# 程式碼如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-112">When deserializing, the C# code resembles the following:</span></span>  
  
```  
MyChoice mc = (MyChoice) myXmlSerializer.Deserialize(myReader);  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne)  
 {  
     // Handle choice one.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceTwo)  
 {  
     // Handle choice two.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType != null)  
 {  
     throw CreateUnknownTypeException(mc.Item);  
 }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-113">還有第二個案例時<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-113">There is a second scenario when the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-114">在下列結構描述中，成員會傳回陣列的項目欄位 (maxOccurs ="unbounded")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-114">In the following schema, the member is a field that returns an array of items (maxOccurs="unbounded").</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-115">陣列可以包含物件的第一個選擇 ("D-a-t-a")，以及第二個選項 ("MoreData")。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-115">The array can contain objects of the first choice ("D-a-t-a"), and of the second choice ("MoreData").</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="D-a-t-a" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="MoreData" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-116">然後，產生的類別會使用欄位來傳回項目的陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-116">The resulting class then uses a field to return an array of items.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-117">每個項目的陣列，對應中`ItemChoiceType`也必須找到列舉型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-117">For each item in the array, a corresponding `ItemChoiceType` enumeration must also be found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-118">比對的列舉型別包含在所傳回的陣列`ItemsElementName`欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-118">The matching enumerations are contained in the array returned by the `ItemsElementName` field.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class MyChoice {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("D-a-t-a", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("MoreData", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute("ItemsElementName")]  
 public string[] Items;  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute(IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlIgnoreAttribute()]  
 public ItemsChoiceType[] ItemsElementName;  
}  
[System.Xml.Serialization.XmlTypeAttribute(IncludeInSchema=false)]  
public enum ItemsChoiceType {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlEnumAttribute("D-a-t-a")]  
 Data,  
 MoreData,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-119">還原序列化物件，其中包含一組選項，當使用控制結構 (例如 if...then...else 結構) 來判斷要還原序列化特定值的方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-119">When deserializing an object that includes a range of choices, use a control structure (such as an if...then...else structure) to determine how to deserialize a particular value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-120">在控制項結構中，檢查列舉值，並據以還原序列化的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-120">In the control structure, check the enumeration value and deserialize the value accordingly.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-121">下列範例會序列化類別，名為`Choices`包含兩個欄位`MyChoice`和`ManyChoices`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-121">The following example serializes a class named `Choices` that includes two fields, `MyChoice` and `ManyChoices`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-122"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute>套用至指定的每個欄位 (透過<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A>屬性)，取得或設定列舉型別所偵測到此成員值的另一個類別成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-122">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to each field that specifies (through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property) another class member that gets or sets an enumeration that detects the member value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-123">`MyChoice`欄位可以設定為單一值，以對應中找到的列舉型別成員`EnumType`欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-123">The `MyChoice` field can be set to a single value, with a corresponding enumeration member found in the `EnumType` field.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-124">`ManyChoices`欄位會傳回物件的陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-124">The `ManyChoices` field returns an array of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-125">`ChoiceArray`欄位會傳回列舉值的陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-125">The `ChoiceArray` field returns an array of enumeration values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6b55b-126">每一個陣列成員`ManyChoices`欄位中，找到對應的成員所傳回陣列中`ChoiceArray`欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6b55b-126">For each array member in the `ManyChoices` field, a corresponding member is found in the array returned by the `ChoiceArray` field.</span></span>  
  
